    {
      "id": "page-HushNotes-project",
      "title": "HushNotes",
      "icon": "auto_stories",
      "parentId": "page-projects",
      "order": 0,
      "createdAt": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-04-03T00:00:00Z",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "b-ws1",
          "type": "heading1",
          "content": "HushNotes \u2014 Project Log"
        },
        {
          "id": "b-ws2",
          "type": "callout",
          "content": "\ud83c\udf89 This is the project that created the very app you are reading this in.",
          "variant": "success"
        },
        {
          "id": "b-ws3",
          "type": "heading2",
          "content": "Why I Built This"
        },
        {
          "id": "b-ws4",
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "Every note-taking app I tried \u2014 Notion, Obsidian cloud sync, Confluence \u2014 had the same problem: my data lived somewhere I did not fully control. I wanted something that felt like Notion but worked like a local file. So I built HushNotes: a React app that reads and writes a single JSON file, runs entirely in the browser, and never phones home."
        },
        {
          "id": "b-ws5",
          "type": "heading2",
          "content": "Tech Stack"
        },
        {
          "id": "b-ws6",
          "type": "table",
          "content": "",
          "tableData": {
            "headers": [
              "Layer",
              "Technology"
            ],
            "rows": [
              [
                "Frontend",
                "React (Create React App)"
              ],
              [
                "State",
                "useState / useCallback / useRef hooks"
              ],
              [
                "IDs",
                "uuid (v4)"
              ],
              [
                "Styling",
                "Custom CSS with CSS variables for theming"
              ],
              [
                "Data persistence",
                "Local JSON file \u2014 no database, no backend"
              ],
              [
                "Search",
                "In-memory full-text search across all blocks"
              ],
              [
                "Drag & Drop",
                "HTML5 drag events, custom implementation"
              ]
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "b-ws7",
          "type": "heading2",
          "content": "Key Design Decisions"
        },
        {
          "id": "b-ws8",
          "type": "bulletList",
          "items": [
            {
              "id": "kd1",
              "text": "Block-based editor \u2014 every piece of content is a typed block, making the format extensible"
            },
            {
              "id": "kd2",
              "text": "Single JSON file \u2014 the entire knowledge base is one portable file you can version-control or back up to a USB drive"
            },
            {
              "id": "kd3",
              "text": "No auto-save \u2014 deliberate save-on-demand so you control when data.json changes"
            },
            {
              "id": "kd4",
              "text": "Lock mode \u2014 toggle read-only so you can browse without accidentally editing"
            },
            {
              "id": "kd5",
              "text": "Dark/Light theme \u2014 CSS variable system makes theming trivial"
            },
            {
              "id": "kd6",
              "text": "Infinite page nesting \u2014 sidebar supports arbitrary depth via parentId references"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "b-ws9",
          "type": "heading2",
          "content": "Shipped Features"
        },
        {
